m gatherings of knowledge. Malik wrote back to him, \u201cAllah Almighty has distributed good deeds just as he has distributed provision. A man\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19468,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/09\/malik-sunnah-my-opinion\/","url_meta":{"origin":24920,"position":3},"title":"Malik on Sunnah: If my opinion contradicts Sunnah, leave it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 9, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abdul Barr reported: Malik ibn Anas, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cI am only a human being. I make mistakes and I am correct, so investigate my opinions. Whatever agrees with the Book and the Sunnah, take it. Whatever does not agree with them, abandon it.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21964,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/02\/18\/salaf-seeker-ilm-stop-learning\/","url_meta":{"origin":24920,"position":4},"title":"Salaf on Learning: Not befitting seeker of knowledge to stop learning","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 18, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Manadhir reported: I asked Abu 'Amr ibn al-Ala', may Allah have mercy on him, \u201cFor how long is it appropriate for a man to learn?\u201d Abu 'Amr said, \u201cIt is appropriate for him to learn his entire life.\u201d Sufyan ibn 'Uyaynah, may Allah have mercy on him, was asked,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":10171,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/12\/10\/malik-fiqh-force-caliph\/","url_meta":{"origin":24920,"position":5},"title":"Malik on Fiqh: Imam Malik does not force his school on Muslims","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 10, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn 'Abdul Barr reported: Imam Malik ibn Anas, may Allah have mercy upon him, said: When the Caliph Abu Ja\u2019far al-Mansur performed the pilgrimage, he called for me, so I entered upon him and he spoke to me, asking me questions, and I replied. Then, he said, \u201cI am determined\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/24920","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=24920"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/24920\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https: